Okay.

00:32:32.240 --> 00:32:38.020
So part of what we wanted to do with this release was make uv sort of self-bootstrapping,

00:32:38.380 --> 00:32:39.840
which sounds complicated.

00:32:40.040 --> 00:32:43.360
But the idea there is if you don't have Python installed,

