00:32:51.480 --> 00:32:52.600
and you give us a Python version,

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:54.640
if you don't have any Python installed,

00:32:54.710 --> 00:32:55.940
if you don't have that version installed,

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:57.940
we will download and install it for you.

00:32:58.290 --> 00:33:00.200
